### Vérifier les capacités du serveur
GET http://localhost:3000/capabilities

### Sauvegarder un contexte avec métadonnées
POST http://localhost:3000/context
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "exampleKey",
  "value": "exampleValue",
  "metadata": {
    "type": "configuration",
    "timestamp": "2025-04-20T12:00:00Z",
    "source": "test"
  }
}

### Opération batch
POST http://localhost:3000/context/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "key": "batch1",
    "value": "value1",
    "metadata": {
      "type": "test",
      "timestamp": "2025-04-20T12:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "key": "batch2",
    "value": "value2",
    "metadata": {
      "type": "test",
      "timestamp": "2025-04-20T12:00:00Z"
    }
  }
]

### Récupérer un contexte
GET http://localhost:3000/context/exampleKey

### Mettre à jour un contexte existant
POST http://localhost:3000/context
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "exampleKey",
  "value": "nouvelleValeur"
}

### Vérifier la mise à jour
GET http://localhost:3000/context/exampleKey

### Tester une clé inexistante
GET http://localhost:3000/context/cleInexistante
